node.text: Woah your artworks are truly amazing, I love your artstyle!💛

Feeling loved for so many reasons, but being the foodie that I am, being fed awesome food is definitely an important one 🤣
.
A couple of days ago, I tasted my first açai bowl at work, and fell in love! It was a buckini bowl (swipe for see) from @theacaicollective, sponsored by @snackboxdiaries, and organised by @drjadekua (hmmmm apparently cannot post photos at work so I post my illustrations, can? 😂).
. 
Thank you Clare and @c0rde for your support for frontliners, and thank you Dr Jade for looking out for your juniors. Go show them some love! ❤️
.
If açai bowls are your thing, go to my stories for a wallpaper you can screenshoot! 🥰 .
Also, we NEED an açai bowl emoji, no??? 🤣❤️
. .
.
Stay strong and stay safe, my dears! ❤️
.
.
